            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">10. A 30-year-old man presents to his GP with a 1-week history of painful, swollen knees and a painful right heel. Further history reveals that he has been experiencing burning pains while urinating for the past 2 weeks and that his eyes have become red and itchy. What is the most likely diagnosis?</p>"
